ll here.”"},{"s":45.52,"e":47.5,"text":"I touch the table, I count to five,"},{"s":47.5,"e":49.26,"text":"Name what’s real, remember I’m alive."},{"s":49.26,"e":50.98,"text":"One lamp glowing, one door closed,"},{"s":50.98,"e":52.64,"text":"One heart beating, one calm road."},{"s":52.64,"e":54.34,"text":"Not every sound is a warning,"},{"s":54.26,"e":55.72,"text":"Not every silence is deep."},{"s":55.98,"e":57.78,"text":"Sometimes the night is just nighttime,"},{"s":57.92,"e":59.08,"text":"Sometimes I just need sleep."},{"s":59.64,"e":60.92,"text":"Nothing’s chasing me,"},{"s":60.92,"e":62.64,"text":"I can let it be."},{"s":62.64,"e":64.52,"text":"Clouds pass over,"},{"s":64.58,"e":66,"text":"But they don’t own me."},{"s":66.22,"e":67.68,"text":"I don’t have to fight"},{"s":68.12,"e":69.26,"text":"Every thought I see."},{"s":69.24,"e":71.1,"text":"I breathe once, breathe twice,"},{"s":71.1,"e":74.16,"text":"Come back home to me."},{"s":74.16,"e":75.96,"text":"If my thoughts get loud, I won’t bow down,"},{"s":75.96,"e":77.42,"text":"I’ll turn the volume of the fear back down."},{"s":77.42,"e":79.08,"text":"I’ll call a friend, drink some water slow,"},{"s":79.08,"e":80.76,"text":"Open the window, let the cold air flow."},{"s":80.76,"e":82.52,"text":"No need to solve the whole world tonight,"},{"s":82.52,"e":84.26,"text":"No need to prove every feeling right."},{"s":84.26,"e":85.58,"text":"I can rest, I can pause, I can stay,"},{"s":85.58,"e":87.76,"text":"Let the panic dissolve away."},{"s":88.36,"e":91.22,"text":"I am not trapped in the noise,"},{"s":91.22,"e":94.78,"text":"I still have my name and my voice."},{"s":94.98,"e":98.5,"text":"This moment is smaller than it seems,"},{"s":98.5,"e":101.5,"text":"I can wake up from anxious dreams."},{"s":101.5,"e":104.78,"text":"Hand on chest, count three,"},{"s":104.78,"e":107.98,"text":"There is still a place for me."},{"s":107.98,"e":111.86,"text":"Hand on chest, count four,"},{"s":111.86,"e":116.72,"text":"I don’t need to run anymore."},{"s":117.76,"e":119.18,"text":"Nothing’s chasing me,"},{"s":119.2,"e":120.94,"text":"I can let it be."},{"s":120.94,"e":122.82,"text":"Clouds pass over,"},{"s":122.84,"e":124.3,"text":"But they don’t own me."},{"s":124.3,"e":126.02,"text":"I don’t have to fight"},{"s":126.48,"e":127.56,"text":"Every thought I see."},{"s":127.56,"e":129.36,"text":"I breathe once, breathe twice,"},{"s":129.36,"e":132.5,"text":"Come back home to me."},{"s":133.31,"e":136.34,"text":"Breathe in slow, breathe out clean,"},{"s":136.34,"e":139.42,"text":"I’m right here, I’m not between."},{"s":139.54,"e":143.16,"text":"Feet on floor, eyes on light,"},{"s":143.16,"e":146.5,"text":"I am safe inside tonight."}],"duration":168,"source":"whisper-aligned","generatedAt":"2026-05-25T06:38:40.317Z","stats":{"whisperWords":370,"polishedWords":368,"matched":360,"matchRate":0.978}}